<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>A nice little attcker when you solo, one on one with another creature. This pet absoulutly sucks in any other senario. I have found that this pet is a waste of manna and bonechips when grouped. As I have learned, Ogre SK pets are weak at best, so if you use your pet, you tank for him not the other way around. Works out ok if your Taunt is good enough to save the little guys neck.<BR>
